column5: Hi guys. Do you know if docks are clean of the ice? Thanks.
There are open spots that you can fish from the shore.Did see one fella trying his luck today.You still cant launch.  Soon,very soon.
Update for you Cosmos.  Ice almost gone.guys fishing from the inside spit break wall,dock J.They were nailing them there this morning.  Minnows and Gulp baits.  Hope that helps ya out.
marina is open and out in the bay ther is just slush remaining couple hundred feet from shore, one more day and it should all be gone"
